
## Useful Shorcuts

### View Shortcuts
Ctrl+K Ctrl+S

## Change Themes
Ctrl+K Ctrl+T

## Open Terminal
Ctrl+`

## Select all content in file
Ctrl+a

## Show/Hide side folder explorer bar
Ctrl+B

## Switch between code editos tabs
Ctrl+1, Ctrl+2, Ctrl+3

## Markdown preview
Ctrl+K V

## Coment pice of code
Ctrl+K+C

## Uncommnt
Ctrl+K+U

## Modify Font Size
https://dev-pages.info/vscode-how-to-change-the-font-size/
- nano  $HOME/.config/Code/User/settings.json
	"editor.fontSize": 12,
	"terminal.integrated.fontSize": 12

